Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:23.78,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}かけがえのないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:28.33,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}やさしさの夢
