Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明心里很清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运是无法改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还做这种梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我梦到的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在这里干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不见我的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.34,0:21:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于理我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱内
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.99,0:22:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 弟弟君 早上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥好慢 我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来叫醒我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:22:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 由梦你不能选择自己做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 今天轮到哥哥你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.43,0:23:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 就这种事记得清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.16,0:23:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎鸡蛋可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.39,0:23:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩 不快点的话 要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
